CatDescriptText: Headline for related images published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 28, 1958, page A11, reads: "Alphas Host Brilliant 30th Anniversary Ball"
TitMainTitle: Group of men wearing light colored dinner jackets, dark bow ties, and dark sashes with light colored strip, standing around microphone with stand, in ballroom of Hotel Webster Hall with Corinthian columns, checkerboard floor, large pendant ceiling fixtures, brocade patterned curtain, and sign inscribed "Commemorating Alpha Omicron Lambda's 30th Anniversary 1928-1958" for the Alpha Phi Alpha 30th Anniversary ball
